---
title: Dukkah Crusted Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Tahini Yoghurt
description: Eat like an Egyptian by adding dukkah to your dinner! Here, we add the tasty mix of seeds and spices to
succulent chicken. Served with roasted veggies and couscous, it's definitely a meal to remember.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
